\textbf{SEIR model ODEs:}
\begin{verbatim}
dS/dt = -beta * S * I / N
dE/dt = beta * S * I / N - sigma * E
dI/dt = sigma * E - gamma * I
dR/dt = gamma * I
\end{verbatim}

